OL,3,CDangerous driver admits killing mum
OL,4,Cand daughter on school run
OL,6,FA dangerous driver has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto killing a mother and her daughter
OL,8,Fas they walked to school.
OL,10,FJustyna Hulboj, 27, and four-year-old
OL,11,FLena Czepczo suffered fatal injuries
OL,12,Fwhen they were knocked down on Scott
OL,13,FHall Road, in Sheepscar, Leeds, on the
OL,14,Fmorning of 16 January 2023.
OL,16,FHardeep Bhachu, 27, of Grant Row,
OL,17,FLeeds, appeared at Leeds Crown Court
OL,18,Fon Thursday, 27 June, charged with two
OL,19,Fcounts of causing death by dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving.
