OL,3,CDangerous driver admits killing mum
OL,4,Cand daughter on school run
OL,6,FHe was driving an Audi TT car which
OL,7,Fwas involved in the incident.
OL,9,FBhachu admitted both charges.
OL,11,FAnother man, Jasskamal Riyat, aged 35,
OL,12,Fof Buckstone Avenue, Leeds, faces the
OL,13,Fsame charges.
OL,15,FHe pleaded not guilty at the same
OL,16,Fhearing. A provisional trial date was
OL,17,Fset for 6 January 2025.
OL,19,FBhachu will be sentenced following the
OL,20,Fconclusion of any trial. He was
OL,21,Fremanded in custody.
